item.title: Pen Wishlist
item.description: This is my pen wishlist. I’m looking to acquire all of the following pens, so if you have one for sale, please get in contact with me. Namiki Emperor (old or new nib) Armando Simoni Club Bologna Extra Arco Wahl Eversharp Decoband Superflex (the new model) Sailor KOP with inverted 2-tone nib (primary silver; gold lines) (Asian Way is the only one I know of) Looking for some sort of Danitrio to start the Danitrio section of my collection Visconti Homo Sapiens Bronze Age Maxi w/ 2-tone nib (surprisingly hard to track doWn these days) Namiki Yukari Milky Way Sailor KOP Pro Gear
